Subject: [TSMC] FSAC Bulk import error
Description:
In the message “it will be displayed, Failed to import SA_FSAC_ProcessNames: SQL logic error no such table: TBL_FSAC_ProcessNames”
What is the cause of this
What_We_Know__c: FSAC Bulk Import failed because there was no data to be imported.
Solution_Comment__c: FSAC Bulk Import failed stating that there is nothing to import. It also showed references to FSAC tables in DB. It was determined that the FSAC Scan Job was not run before running this job. After running the job, the issue was resolved. The Customer also wanted the ability to run jobs via API. FR 43847581 has been filed.
